  "description": "Unlike other beat 'em ups, <i>Bloody Roar</i> has a unique twist. At a press of a button, your character changes into a beast of unique strength and ability over the characters normal attacks. Each character has his/her own beast to transform into, and most battles come down to how you use this transformation to your advantage. <br><br>The same style of <a id=\"d616861ed850d60fcbc728ce666224e1d\" href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=tekken\">Tekken</a>, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/street-fighter\">Street Fighter</a> and <a id=\"dce1c9b8ae789ed16d3be944b69f4a4d8\" href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=dead+or+alive\">Dead or Alive</a> is also re-lived, with over-the-top special moves and combos in a 3D like atmosphere.",
